@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Home - AI";
}
<body id="page-top">
 
    <!-- Mashead header-->
    <header class="masthead">
        <div class="container px-5">
            <div class="row gx-5 align-items-center">
                <div class="col-lg-6">
                    <!-- Mashead text and app badges-->
                    <div class="mb-5 mb-lg-0 text-center text-lg-start">
                        <h1 class="display-1 lh-1 mb-3">Welcome to my website on AI</h1>
                        <p class="lead fw-normal text-muted mb-5">Feel free to browse what I have put together and interact with parts of the website. Welcome to the new age of tech, and my hobby.</p>
                        <div class="d-flex flex-column flex-lg-row align-items-center">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-lg-6">
                    <!-- Masthead device mockup feature-->
                    <div class="masthead-device-mockup">
                        <img class="img-fluid" src="/img/reaching_out.jpg" alt="..." style="height:80%; width:80%;" />
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Quote/testimonial aside-->
    <aside class="text-center bg-gradient-primary-to-secondary">
        <div class="container px-5">
            <div class="row gx-5 justify-content-center">
                <div class="col-xl-8">
                    <div class="h2 fs-1 text-white mb-4">"I know the future of humanity can only be secured by correctly integrating advanced artificial intelligence into our society. That is only the first step, but it will help us with the rest."</div>
                    <div class="h1 fs-1 text-white mb-4">-Noah Hicks</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </aside>
    <br />
    <!-- Quote/testimonial aside-->
    <aside class="text-center bg-gradient-primary-to-secondary">
        <div class="container px-5">
            <div class="row gx-5 justify-content-center">
                <div class="col-xl-8">
                    <div class="h2 fs-1 text-white mb-4">"Together, we embark on a journey where artificial intelligence becomes a catalyst for human achievement, illuminating paths to discovery and paving the way for a future where technology and humanity coexist in harmony, fostering an era of unparalleled growth and understanding."</div>
                    <div class="h1 fs-1 text-white mb-4">-GPT 4, in reference to Noah's quote above.</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </aside>

    <!-- App features section-->
    <section id="features">
        <div class="container px-5">
            <div class="row gx-5 align-items-center">
                <div class="col-lg-8 order-lg-1 mb-5 mb-lg-0">
                    <div class="container-fluid px-5">
                        <div class="row gx-5">
                            <div class="col-md-6 mb-5">
                                <!-- Feature item-->
                                <div class="text-center">
                                    <h3 class="font-alt">Healthcare and Medical Research</h3>
                                    <p class="text-muted mb-0">AI can transform healthcare by improving diagnostic accuracy, personalizing treatment plans, and streamlining administrative processes. In medical research, AI algorithms can analyze vast datasets to identify patterns and insights, speeding up the discovery of new drugs and treatments. AI-driven technologies like machine learning models and natural language processing can assist in early detection of diseases, predict patient outcomes, and optimize healthcare delivery, making it more accessible and effective.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-6 mb-5">
                                <!-- Feature item-->
                                <div class="text-center">
                                    <h3 class="font-alt">Environmental Sustainability</h3>
                                    <p class="text-muted mb-0">AI can play a crucial role in combating climate change and promoting sustainability. Through the analysis of environmental data, AI can help in monitoring deforestation, pollution levels, and wildlife populations. It can optimize energy consumption in buildings and industrial processes, enhance the efficiency of renewable energy systems, and improve waste management practices. AI-driven models can forecast weather and climate patterns with greater accuracy, aiding in the preparation for and mitigation of natural disasters.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-md-6 mb-5 mb-md-0">
                                <!-- Feature item-->
                                <div class="text-center">
                                    <h3 class="font-alt">Education and Learning</h3>
                                    <p class="text-muted mb-0">AI has the potential to revolutionize education by offering personalized learning experiences and making education more accessible. Adaptive learning systems powered by AI can tailor educational content to meet the individual needs and learning paces of students, enhancing engagement and outcomes. AI can also automate administrative tasks, giving educators more time to focus on teaching. Moreover, AI technologies can break down language barriers and provide scalable solutions for global education challenges.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-6">
                                <!-- Feature item-->
                                <div class="text-center">
                                    <h3 class="font-alt">Economic Growth and Job Creation</h3>
                                    <p class="text-muted mb-0">While concerns about AI displacing jobs exist, AI also presents opportunities for economic growth and the creation of new job sectors. By automating routine tasks, AI can free up human workers to focus on more complex, creative, and strategic activities, potentially leading to higher job satisfaction and productivity. AI can drive innovation in industries such as technology, finance, and manufacturing, fostering new business models and services. Additionally, AI can improve decision-making processes and operational efficiencies, contributing to overall economic development.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-4 order-lg-0">
                    <!-- Features section device mockup-->
                    <div class="features-device-mockup">

                                    <div class="px-5 px-sm-0"><img class="img-fluid rounded-circle" src="/img/robot_planting.jpg" alt="..." /></div>
  
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Basic features section-->
    <section class="bg-light">
        <div class="container px-5">
            <div class="row gx-5 align-items-center justify-content-center justify-content-lg-between">
                <div class="col-12 col-lg-5">
                    <h2 class="display-4 lh-1 mb-4">Enter a New Age of Humanity</h2>
                    <p class="lead fw-normal text-muted mb-5 mb-lg-0">We stand on the brink of an unprecedented era where the symbiosis between humans and artificial intelligence heralds a renaissance of innovation and prosperity. This vision is not just about leveraging AI to streamline operations or enhance productivity; it's about fundamentally redefining the partnership between humans and machines to unlock creative potential and forge new paradigms in business and society. As we navigate this transformative journey, AI serves as a beacon, guiding us toward solutions that were once deemed impossible, fostering environments where human ingenuity and machine intelligence combine to solve complex challenges. This collaborative future promises not only to elevate businesses to new heights of efficiency and insight but also to cultivate a world where technology amplifies human capability, ensuring a thriving society rich in opportunity, creativity, and shared success. In this new age, our relationship with AI becomes a testament to our adaptability and a cornerstone for a flourishing humanity.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-8 col-md-6">
                    <div class="px-5 px-sm-0"><img class="img-fluid rounded-circle" src="/img/human_ai_interaction.jpg" alt="..." /></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <!-- Call to action section-->
    <section class="cta">
        <div class="cta-content">
            <div class="container px-5">
                <h2 class="text-white display-1 lh-1 mb-4">
                    Talk to my Chat Bot!
                </h2>
                <a class="btn btn-outline-light py-3 px-4 rounded-pill" asp-area="" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Chat">Chat</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>


</body>

